item.description: Rachel Mochizuki is currently a fourth-year undergraduate student pursuing a Biopsychology degree at UC Santa Barbara. She joined the lab in January 2021 to conduct her senior honors thesis. Her research will focus on how the severity of visual impairment affects quality of life.
